<h1>Articles</h1>

Our blog has <%= Article.public_count %> 
<%= (Article.public_count > 1 || Article.public_count == 0) ? 'articles' : 'article' %> 
and counting!

<ul>
  <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <% unless article.archived? %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>
